---
tags: [ packaging ]
---
# Install a specific package:
dnf install "<package>"

# Find packages matching a specific phrase:
dnf search "<phrase>"

# Find which package provides a specific executable:
dnf provides "<executable>"

# The following are available after installing "dnf-plugins-core"

# Download a specific package:
dnf download "<package>"

# Install the build dependencies for a SRPM or from a .spec file:
dnf builddep <path/to/file>
